constituent: levy, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight, warrior, one, stop, footprint, arrow
heisigStory: A certain portion of shells (money) is collected by the warrior from the local villages as he passes through to defray the costs of keeping the land safe, and this is called a levy.
koohiiStory1: A warrior stands guard at a bridge collecting shells as a levy for any who want to pass.
koohiiStory2: Drove my Chevy to the levy but the levy was dry. And those good old warrior boys, drinking whiskey and rye, said pay up the clams or you´ll die. Pay up the clams or you´ll die....
myStory: thuế. chiến binh và vỏ sò
